{"title": [], "abstractContent": [{"text": "Machine translation (MT) has been studied for more than 60 years.", "labels": [], "entities": [{"text": "Machine translation (MT)", "start_pos": 0, "end_pos": 24, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.916684353351593}]}, {"text": "World-Wide-Web offers more opportunities to MT.", "labels": [], "entities": [{"text": "World-Wide-Web", "start_pos": 0, "end_pos": 14, "type": "DATASET", "confidence": 0.9287937879562378}, {"text": "MT", "start_pos": 44, "end_pos": 46, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.9905141592025757}]}, {"text": "We could try to crawl more web data to train the MT system.", "labels": [], "entities": [{"text": "MT", "start_pos": 49, "end_pos": 51, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.9732062816619873}]}, {"text": "But we have to filter the very noisy web data.", "labels": [], "entities": []}, {"text": "There are many potential web-based applications for MT, such as translation of web-page, translation of instant message, translation of SNS, translation of ecommerce, mobile translation, etc.", "labels": [], "entities": [{"text": "MT", "start_pos": 52, "end_pos": 54, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.9954177141189575}, {"text": "translation of web-page", "start_pos": 64, "end_pos": 87, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.8686184287071228}, {"text": "translation of instant message", "start_pos": 89, "end_pos": 119, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.8594778180122375}, {"text": "translation of SNS", "start_pos": 121, "end_pos": 139, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.8790458043416342}, {"text": "translation of ecommerce", "start_pos": 141, "end_pos": 165, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.8918734391530355}, {"text": "mobile translation", "start_pos": 167, "end_pos": 185, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.7150115966796875}]}, {"text": "To make better use of the web data, and to produce better webbased MT applications, we should also adapt the MT methods to the web scenario.", "labels": [], "entities": [{"text": "MT", "start_pos": 67, "end_pos": 69, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.9162569046020508}, {"text": "MT", "start_pos": 109, "end_pos": 111, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.9725792407989502}]}, {"text": "In this talk, I will introduce our work on web-based machine translation.", "labels": [], "entities": [{"text": "machine translation", "start_pos": 53, "end_pos": 72, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.6905957013368607}]}], "introductionContent": [], "datasetContent": [], "tableCaptions": []}